                    &nbsp;|&nbsp;
            <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/section/opinion/columns">COLUMNS</a></span></div>

                <h1>An open letter to the Class of 2023</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/ece40b6b-9187-4128-b861-144d4f5fe9e8.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Prospective&#x20;freshmen&#x20;walk&#x20;around&#x20;the&#x20;Engineering&#x20;Quad&#x20;while&#x20;on&#x20;a&#x20;campus&#x20;tour&#x20;Thursday&#x20;for&#x20;Blue&#x20;Devil&#x20;Days." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            Prospective freshmen walk around the Engineering Quad while on a campus tour Thursday for Blue Devil Days.

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
